<script setup lang="ts">
defineProps({
  label: {
    type: String,
    required: true
  },
  name: {
    type: String,
    required: true
  },
  placeholder: {
    type: String,
    default: null
  },
  required: {
    type: Boolean,
    default: true
  }
})
</script>

<template>
  <Field :label="label">
    <textarea
      :name="name"
      :required="required"
      :placeholder="placeholder"
      class="h-40 w-full rounded-none border-b border-slate-200 py-3 pr-7 pl-3 text-slate-800 placeholder-slate-400"
    />
  </Field>
</template>
